{"id":19174,"title":"[The first department of infectious diseases in Russia: history of formation, main achievements and prospects of the national infectology].","abstract":"Russian first department of infectious diseases, which has great traditions and achievements, as of right is a brilliant constellation of national researchers and practitioners military infectology, not only brought the Kirov Military Medical Academy into repute, but also made a huge contribution to the development of the science of infectious diseases and the establishment of an effective system treatment and prevention of these diseases. This article outlines the main historical stages of infectology in the armed forces of our country, summed up the contribution of members of the Department of Infectious Diseases of the Military Medical Academy in medical science, marked modern progress and prospects of development of military infectology.","date":"2014-04-17","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24738284","annotations":[{"name":"Russia","weight":0.91782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russia"},{"name":"Infectious disease","weight":0.85687,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infectious_disease"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"History","weight":0.587437,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.582424,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Science","weight":0.579145,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science"},{"name":"Military","weight":0.571804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military"},{"name":"Armed forces","weight":0.445789,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armed_forces"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.42745,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Russian langua